  "detailed_description": "Hikikomori No Chuunibyou is a pseudo 8-bit platform-adventure game with beat-em-up, puzzle, and stealth elements. With its storytelling directing the player through open-ended levels, progression through each stage requires usage of parkour-like abilities and martial-arts techniques.<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Parkour-inspired platforming<br></li><li>    Open-ended levels with story-focused progression<br></li><li>    Beat-em-up, puzzle, and stealth elements<br></li><li>    Unlimited continues and frequent checkpoints<br></li><li>    8-bit graphics and soundtrack<br></li><li>    Supports Xbox 360 Controller (recommended)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Hikikomori No Chuunibyou is a pseudo 8-bit platform-adventure game with beat-em-up, puzzle, and stealth elements. With its storytelling directing the player through open-ended levels, progression through each stage requires usage of parkour-like abilities and martial-arts techniques.<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    Parkour-inspired platforming<br></li><li>    Open-ended levels with story-focused progression<br></li><li>    Beat-em-up, puzzle, and stealth elements<br></li><li>    Unlimited continues and frequent checkpoints<br></li><li>    8-bit graphics and soundtrack<br></li><li>    Supports Xbox 360 Controller (recommended)</li></ul>",
